title: march 26: James Cameron sinks to the bottom of the sea (with Tune-Yards)
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about director James Cameron’s historic solo dive to Earth’s lowest point, Challenger Deep in the Mariana Trench, as well as a bit about Cameron’s film credits and the mission that led him to the depths of the Pacific Ocean. Afterwards, she is joined by special guest Tune-Yards. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
